 "prompt": "A sleek, minimalist black lightweight padded jacket, gently puffed with invisible warmth., A softly lit, minimalist urban loft interior with large windows overlooking a city., A stylish, confident young adult, 20s-30s, with a modern, sharp hairstyle., LS of character walking towards a large window, turning slightly to show the jacket's elegant drape, Rembrandt lighting, Phase One IQ4, 8k, hyper-realistic --no text, logo",
 "styling": { "style": "aspirational, sophisticated", "color": "urban greys, warm indoor light", "lighting": "Rembrandt, natural window light" }
}
